productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
My dog loves to play with it.
I tried to kidnap it but got apricot all over it.
one of my hobbies is skateboarding. and when i'm skateboarding this works great.
The box this comes in is 3 meter by 6 yard and weights 12 pound.
